Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.96,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}頑な心のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:19.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石ころはどこまで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}砂のように脆く崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一文字も読めない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:32.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}ただ前に進むだけじゃ見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:42.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}言葉の出来ないものを下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一粒の冷たい石に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:49.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}秘められた熱もあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}どうせなら 勝ちに行きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}何もかも見えない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:58.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空っぽのままの心でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}閉ざされた夢を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:12.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}勢い任せで掴んだ手が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:15.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}きっと君を変えてくsignal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}会いたくて 飛んだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}堕ちてゆくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:25.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}もう一度 空を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}放り投げる想いすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}泣いだって 分け合って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}君が笑うまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,866)}stone cold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:00:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}以一顆頑固的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:19.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石塊可以去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如同砂土般輕易崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}無法預知一字的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:28.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:32.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如若只是一味向前則會迷失所有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:42.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}請賜予我無法用語言形容的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一顆冰冷的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:49.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}恐怕也隱藏著炙熱的溫度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}既然已經決定 那就想要取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空無一物的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:58.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:02.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算只有一顆空洞的心也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}追尋緊閉的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:12.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}把一切交給氣勢 握緊的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:15.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}絕對能夠改變你的人生signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如此思念你 哪怕就算飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}也終會墜落消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:25.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}再一次沖上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}抱緊所有拋下的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算哭泣 也一起承擔
