Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據名冊上記載

Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:47.52,OT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}原石的覺醒

Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有267人乘坐在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後全都失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上載著Perseus之像 Euryale之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.27,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perseus 希臘神話中殺死美杜莎的英雄 Euryale希臘神話蛇妖三姐妹之一 美杜莎的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放一起的兩個東西不知道被哪個笨蛋放在了一起啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的對手只靠我們是無法對抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須借助那位大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓他覺醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這也是為了阿爾瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 全部都白費了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安丹童子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說若菜啊 別和他打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話回來啊 怎麼偏偏會是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那傢伙的傳聞都沒什麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有能拿到兩萬元的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你跑去說一句「去死吧 阿爾瑪」就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 作為懲罰你要付一萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家很有錢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 你還敢這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}啊 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事嗎 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在這種地方虛度光陰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒防備了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我邀請你進礦石部這事 你考慮過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}我不加入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回答得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學你不是經常在河邊撿石頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天啊 大家要一起去美術館
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊庭院裡的石頭啊 超可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得丹童子同學你一定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別說這種話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 這孩子腦子稍微有點短路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在日出公園門口的車站等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦 若菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}5點半在那裡等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等你來的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說若菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去和那種傢伙搭話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種男人加入礦石部裡的話會很麻煩的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經把混混們都送進醫院了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是發火了不知道會做出什麼事來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那不是傳聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒見過他做過什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 經常在河邊撿石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曰「愛石之人絕非惡人」喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路A封鎖完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路B封鎖完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路C封鎖完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 在任務結束前就這樣先待機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊班 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,point alpha 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,point bravo 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊命令由現場發出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等待訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 準備已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是丹童子阿爾瑪先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是藍羽財團的CEO 藍羽瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是管家鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼瓦啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望您能將力量借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天在三浦半島的海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘大型貨船發生爆炸並被燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事是由被我們稱為「惡石」的怪物引發的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 「惡石」將會帶來更大的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒它們 我們需要您的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是什麼傳銷的話就請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生 請將您沉睡這的力量借給我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道妳在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您在三年前所使用的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想隱瞞也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們對於你的事瞭若指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子阿爾瑪 17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新港學園2年級 成績中等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暴力事件中將18名高中生打傷至住院8個月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了停學半年的處分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在保護觀察中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親在未婚狀態下出產
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十年前由於事故而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後保護人由…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你們有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別和我扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生 請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了別管我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bravo 瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha 瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 糟糕了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的力量超出了我的想像啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻離開那裡啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會被全滅的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和我…扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 暫時先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃 再去找他可能會被殺掉的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 最糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是明戶二號大街 怪物正向這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口騷動不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很吵鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若菜 真的要等那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 隨便妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「惡石」好像再次開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻進入警戒狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 準備好運輸兵和契約裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.91,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「惡石」確認 「惡石」確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「惡石」在臨海公園現身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正向東南方以時速3公里移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升機飛往指定座標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請報座標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35 point 7719
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,139 point 6361
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約10分鐘後到達指定座標
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現得晚了啊 鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪阿爾瑪 對「惡石」的感應變遲鈍了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在日出公園門口的車站等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和我扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等著的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動起來！我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口不停地騷動著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生 把惡石前進方向上與原石有關的資料發給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我有關這裡的更詳細資料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 森園美術館對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.11,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stheno 蛇妖三姐妹之一 美杜莎的另一個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Stheno之瞳正在那裡展出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就糟了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美杜莎有兩個擁有不死之力的姐姐啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是Euryale
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個就是Stheno
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美杜莎已經得到了Euryale的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連Stheno的力量都得到了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 看起來好貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說要5億
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不論庭院裡的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有這個我們也來得值了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通知告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請避難離開會場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先聯絡下若菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 揚羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒訊號了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請妳們去避難巴士上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線上的避難狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在漸漸進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stheno之瞳的採購呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出了高於原價兩倍的金額
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是持有者卻不答應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是提到三倍金額還不答應的話就收手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美杜莎到達Stheno之瞳前 由我打敗它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了以防萬一 去和阿爾瑪接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妳還相信那傢伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 請帶上狙擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃 妳的生命很危險喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能在此拯救他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就失去擁有力量的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 我也會拼盡全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回府邸了 去掩護大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才收到了一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像現在橫須賀市內發出了特別事態宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民們開始進行避難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的小林記者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底現在情況怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察並沒有發出聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所見 從剛才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市內就斷斷續續冒出火與煙氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 那邊交通管制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有傷到它一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約裝甲 主控系統失效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動輔助系統
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「惡石」的狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正大幅脫離警戒範圍進行移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標變成瑠璃了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是想把瑠璃和吊墜兩個都吃了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為比起Euryale 這塊原石更具有力量啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是吃了瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真得能成不死之身了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會讓這種事得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉地趕不上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為他會來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 阿爾瑪先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 日出町上空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見美杜莎和丹童子阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻惡石交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在5分鐘後也能到達了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣給我先待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐一定會亂來 不快點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳負責救助傷患和叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然惡石不過是惡石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 清醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了同樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量會傷害他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼應該消失的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就喚醒你真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒Sacred Seven的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之記憶聚集我身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之意識賜予你身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我…真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡先生 Stheno的採購失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪心不足蛇吞象啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個超級大的惡石跳去瑠璃妳那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 妳的「意識」我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得找個無人區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪 同時破壞那兩個核心啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時破壞兩個的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老子粉碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦震盪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其他都是些擦傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 丹童子要是再來早一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 只要他來了 我就OK了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他好像肯加入礦石部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做這種無聊事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝謝你 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然居然 今天還有別的想要入部的人也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能跟阿爾瑪先生在一起所以我入部了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們不是這裡的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 我是這個學校的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大人是理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我怕麻煩啦 所以就把學校給買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES 真的啊鬼

